text: Jeshua, tangada Levi, mo ana dama daane mo ono gau, mo Kadmiel mo ana dama daane ala go di madahaanau o Hodaviah guu buni ngaadahi bolo ga madamada humalia mo di dagi digau ala e hau haga hoou di Hale Daumaha deelaa. Gei ogo digau Levi mai i di madahaanau o Henadad gu hagamaamaa labelaa digaula.
